title: Bindr
description: Bindr is designed as an AI-powered, user-friendly web application that provides students with an interactive, personalized tool to organize study material, practice concepts, and keep track of deadlines.

title: League of Legends Ban Rate Analysis
description: An in-depth data science project conducted at UCSD that dives into exploratory data analysis, hypothesis testing, baseline model development, and fairness assessment of the tournaments of this game.

title: Wheel of Fortune Analysis
description: An statistical approach to solving the most likely characters to appear in the final round of the American game show, Wheel of Fortune, using frequency analysis and NLP techniques.

title: US Energy Overview
description: This project analyzes time-series energy data from Energy Information Administration from 1949 until 2024, with the goal of forecasting future energy consumption. The analysis includes interactive visualizations and forecasting using Holt-Winter models.
